{"tid":2031551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post]524口號要簡單直接","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:44:35.000Z","uid":148795,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dcda93850597737a9ab460e8d014bbc3902f25c8","tid":2031551,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR:<br />\n一國兩制 名存實亡<br />\n拒絕國安 制裁中共</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口號唔使好聽，只需要簡單直接，你要明白外國人唔識聽廣東話、唔會理你押唔押韻，只係睇外媒點譯呢句口號。<br />\n<br />\n「民族自強 香港獨立」個意思其實一早喺外媒已經出現過，所以要有目標清晰嘅口號，話比外國聽香港人唔要國安法，要國際出手制裁。<br />\n<br />\n獨立係長遠目標，聽日行街係有目的地行，就係唔要國安法，要求國際出手，所以嗌獨立口號同時麻煩嗌埋呢啲簡單直接嘅口號唔該<br />\n<br />\n順手推埋個琴晚出嘅post，主旨就係唔好帶啲用唔著嘅嘢增加被咬嘅風險，帶前請考慮成效同成本。<br />\n<br />\n［行動post］524 出去行街嘅入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2030310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2030310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48e2f936f6c43f686c4da283d55c364965fb5a4f","tid":2031551,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"仆街開咗喺吹水台"},{"pid":"2159bf2191c7e41e735f1b9b3c00b307123f6359","tid":2031551,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0abc26525f8ff9c9caef705fa1cdedd63aad9799","tid":2031551,"uid":200895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46a0706f779bce577d8437672b2a608606db061","tid":2031551,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8f07efb465a7902d02fd6c5cb03f9cc53439093","tid":2031551,"uid":25140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66242fcb7fd5ef67f8faef235326388965ee754f","tid":2031551,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e21b7764b54ce72d0c